        </div>
        <div class="w-full md:w-1/5 p-6 flex flex-col flex-grow flex-shrink">
          <div
            class="flex-1 bg-white rounded-t rounded-b-none overflow-hidden shadow"
          >
            <p class="w-full text-gray-600 text-xs md:text-sm px-6 underline">
              01
            </p>
            <div
              class="w-full font-bold text-xl text-gray-800 px-6 pt-5"
            >
              사전준비
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-800 text-base px-6 mb-5 pt-5">
              로그인<br>
              본인 인증
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full md:w-1/5 p-6 flex flex-col flex-grow flex-shrink">
          <div
            class="flex-1 bg-white rounded-t rounded-b-none overflow-hidden shadow"
          >
            <p class="w-full text-gray-600 text-xs md:text-sm px-6 underline">
              02
            </p>
            <div class="w-full font-bold text-xl text-gray-800 px-6 pt-5">
            URL 조회
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-800 text-base px-6 mb-5 pt-5">
              웹 사이트 URL 입력
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full md:w-1/5 p-6 flex flex-col flex-grow flex-shrink">
          <div
            class="flex-1 bg-white rounded-t rounded-b-none overflow-hidden shadow"
          >
            <p class="w-full text-gray-600 text-xs md:text-sm px-6 underline">
              03
            </p>
            <div class="w-full font-bold text-xl text-gray-800 px-6 pt-5">
              진단 진행
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-800 text-base px-6 mb-5 pt-5">
              도구 실행<br>
              웹 취약점 진단
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full md:w-1/5 p-6 flex flex-col flex-grow flex-shrink">
          <div
            class="flex-1 bg-white rounded-t rounded-b-none overflow-hidden shadow"
          >
            <p class="w-full text-gray-600 text-xs md:text-sm px-6 underline">
              04
            </p>
            <div class="w-full font-bold text-xl text-gray-800 px-6 pt-5">
              진단 결과
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-800 text-base px-6 mb-5 pt-5">
              진단 결과분석<br />
              취약점 보완 대책 제시
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full md:w-1/5 p-6 flex flex-col flex-grow flex-shrink">
          <div
            class="flex-1 bg-white rounded-t rounded-b-none overflow-hidden shadow"
          >
            <p class="w-full text-gray-600 text-xs md:text-sm px-6 underline">
              05
            </p>
            <div class="w-full font-bold text-xl text-gray-800 px-6 pt-5">
              보고서 작성
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-800 text-base px-6 mb-5 pt-5">
              PDF 저장
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- url 조회 -->
    <section class="bg-gray-100">
      <div class="container mx-auto flex flex-wrap pt-4 pb-12">
        <div class="w-full p-6 flex flex-col flex-grow flex-shrink mt-7">
          <div
            class="flex-1 bg-white rounded-t rounded-b-none overflow-hidden shadow"
          >
          <h2
            class="w-full my-2 text-5xl font-bold leading-tight text-center text-gray-800"
          >
            URL
          </h2>
          <div class="w-full mb-4">
            <div
              class="h-1 mx-auto gradient w-64 opacity-25 my-0 py-0 rounded-t"
            ></div>
            <p class="text-gray-800 text-base px-6 mb-5 pt-5 text-center">
              <b>점검할 웹 사이트의 URL을 입력해주세요</b>
              <br>
              로그인 후, 진단 서비스를 이용할 수 있습니다
            </p>
            <form class="space-y-4 md:space-y-6" action="/analysis" method="post">
              <div>
                <input
                  type="text"
                  name="url"
                  class="bg-gray-50 border mx-auto border-gray-300 text-gray-900 sm:text-sm rounded-lg block w-3/5 p-2.5"
                  placeholder="URL을 입력해주세요"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
                <button
                  type="submit"
                  class="text-center mx-auto lg:mx-0 bg-green-700 font-bold rounded-full my-6 py-4 px-8 shadow-lg focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline transform transition hover:scale-105 duration-300 ease-in-out"
                >
                  조회
                </button>
              </div>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
